  "text": "where Δ ( ) is the measured ASL difference signal between label and control images in a specified ROI or voxel at inversion time , Δ is the arterial transit time, is the bolus duration, CBF is the cerebral blood flow, 0 is the fully relaxed magnetization of the blood, 1 is the longitudinal relaxation time of the arterial blood, and is the labeling efficiency, assumed to be 0.95 for the hyperbolic secant pulse used in this study [CITATION_1] .",
